snippet.title: Tyd wag vir Niemand (Time waits for Nobody) - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Now Available for PC, Mac and Linux on Steam:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/589730/Tyd_wag_vir_Niemand_Time_waits_for_Nobody/

Tyd wag vir Niemand is an Abstract First Person Adventure where you can manipulate time at will in order to escape deadly traps, perform tricky jumps and overcome a myriad of other challenges, to Ultimately uncover the mystery behind this strange realm you are trapped in.

Tyd wag vir Niemand is Afrikaans for "Time waits for Nobody"
